Conky Radio Livenow
===================

It displays hungarian radio stations' current songs.

Using:
------

If the scripts are saved in ~/scripts add this to .conkyrc:

$hr
${color grey}Juventus:$color ${texeci 15 lua ~/scripts/radio_juventus.lua}
${color grey}MR2:$color ${texeci 15 lua ~/scripts/radio_mr2.lua}
${color grey}NeoFM:$color ${texeci 15 lua ~/scripts/radio_neofm.lua}
${color grey}ClassFM:$color ${texeci 15 lua ~/scripts/radio_classfm.lua}
${color grey}Radio1:$color ${texeci 15 lua ~/scripts/radio_radio1.lua}
$hr